    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this absolute gem. It\u2019s been babied since day one and is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Spotless inside and out, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message and come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, a masterclass in front-midship engineering and 50/50 weight distribution. This specimen retains its original 13B-REW twin-rotor power plant, featuring the sophisticated sequential turbocharging system that delivers seamless boost across the rev range. The chassis remains rigid and unmolested, supported by the factory four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a Torsen limited-slip differential for surgical turn-in precision. Every vacuum line, seal, and apex corner is in peak operational state, with documented compression figures reflecting its pristine internal health. Finished in its factory-original coat with a concours-level interior, this FD represents a rare opportunity to own a pure, analog driving machine in its most refined form.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_3",
